name: MeMailSettings
body:
### Welcome to MeMailSettings page.
MeMailSettings can make your Nokia N9 Email client even better with folder's mapping and few more additional settings. Device reboot might be needed to enable some new features.
tagline: An application that helps to enable some features for Nokia N9 MfE and/or Email accounts.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
